<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Doc-Hub</title>

    <style>
      body {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      ul {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        list-style: none;
      }

      li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>

    <p>
      You're invited you to use Doc-Hub, where you can securely and easily upload documents and files to share
      with your accounting team at NR Accounting & Business Advisors.
    </p>

    <p>
      You can login by visiting this link <a href="{{url}}">{{url}}</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please use the following credentials to login:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Username:</strong> {{email}}</li>
      <li><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Best wishes,<br><b>NR Accounting & Business Advisors Inc.</b></p>
  </body>

</html>
